articles.title: NASA’s Lucy Captures Ice Cream Cone–Shaped Asteroid That Defies Expectations - SciTechDaily
articles.description: NASA’s Lucy spacecraft has captured striking images of asteroid Donaldjohanson, revealing it to be a contact binary with an unusual “ice cream cone” shape. This unexpected geological complexity offers insights into the early solar system. Although not a prima…
